=== STELLAR_CARTOGRAPHER ===
# id: 74
# title: The Stellar Cartographer's Legacy
# chinese_title: 星图师遗产
# category: Lore
# mode: dungeon

A legendary cartographer's private study, perfectly preserved. Star charts line every wall, each annotated with character-based classification systems. Her magnum opus — a unified map of known space encoded entirely in Chinese characters — sits open on the desk, unfinished.

* [Study her classification system]
  ~ gain_radical("田")
  "类" (lèi) — category, type, class
* [Complete a section of the map]
  ~ gain_xp(30)
  "绘" (huì) — to draw, to paint
* [Take a rare chart for trade]
  ~ gain_gold(25)
  "图" (tú) — map, chart, picture
* [Leave everything undisturbed out of respect]
  ~ gain_xp(10)
  "尊" (zūn) — to respect, to honor
